<slide title='MDB Remote Viewer'>
<blurb>
We made a lightweight molecular viewer that is embeddable
by using simple HTML code in a page. For example, the snippet:
</blurb>
<example fontsize='1.5em' result='1'>
<title>This form will display all zinc containing sites in 1hca and
1npc</title>
<text>
<![CDATA[<div align='center'>
<form method="POST"
action="http://metallo.scripps.edu/services/remote/viewer.php"
name="Remote MDB Viewer" target="_blank">
<input type="hidden" name="source_id[]" value="1hca">
<input type="hidden" name="source_id[]" value="1npc">
<input type="hidden" name="metal[]" value="zn">
<input type="hidden" name="caption" value="Zn sites in 1hca and 1npc">
<input type="submit" name="submit" value="Display Zn sites in the MDB Viewer">
</form>
</div>]]>
</text>
</example>
<blurb>
The remote viewer is being used by several web sites, among them:
</blurb>
